{"tid":989872,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"沙拿疑插水！賽後被轟：正毀掉自己的名聲","createTime":"2019-01-21T07:43:50.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-22T09:27:25.000Z","uid":147522,"like":84,"dislike":23,"uniUserReply":39,"replies":[{"pid":"61caf1970203fc533a408782753c4b50c9296038","tid":989872,"uid":147522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-21T07:43:50.000Z","msg":"　　利物浦主場4-3險勝水晶宮，然而賽後沙拿的疑似插水卻成為了球迷們討論的熱點。<br />\n<br />\n　　上半場第39分鐘時，沙拿在水晶宮禁區拿球，在沙高的防守下倒地，但慢鏡頭顯示兩人只有輕微的身體接觸。<br />\n<br />\n　　BBC解說嘉賓、前熱刺前鋒克魯克斯對此感到遺憾：「可悲。人們在禁區裡防守時會攔截你，但你不能這樣糊弄大家，因為你這樣做是在自毀名聲。他正在毀掉自己的聲譽。」<br />\n<br />\n　　「很快，連利物浦球迷也會承認這是插水。」"},{"pid":"d077c3eaf34a9e04a7037af89041daa5d40e156a","tid":989872,"uid":209773,"like":6,"dislike":2,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-21T07:45:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"00ae050f4848e327aa3da4f4c7b8ded7af58f681","tid":989872,"uid":131078,"like":145,"dislike":13,"score":132,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-21T07:47:06.000Z","msg":"拉莫斯搞到佢咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bac85d7f44a6ef78645995777f1c41be2f135991","tid":989872,"uid":147522,"like":21,"dislike":4,"score":17,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-01-21T07:47:32.000Z","msg":"　　「很快，連利物浦球迷也會承認這是插水。」"},{"pid":"436fe241efe0ac3d1a36276e9a5789b867bc1cbc","tid":989872,"uid":872,"like":51,"dislike":1,"score":50,"quote":{"pid":"00ae050f4848e327aa3da4f4c7b8ded7af58f681","tid":989872,"uid":131078,"like":145,"dislike":13,"score":132,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-21T07:47:06.000Z","msg":"拉莫斯搞到佢咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-01-21T07:48:21.000Z","msg":"隻手傷左呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1d0da90833d416ba17a2a5e2b117a2eb24028c4c","tid":989872,"uid":107611,"like":60,"dislike":5,"score":55,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-21T07:48:39.000Z","msg":"唔插水就唔係沙拿啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmo